{"tid":951136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義大利貨輪遭挾持 英軍特種部隊成功奪回","createTime":"2018-12-22T05:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T06:16:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35e17c61bee77fb083f47417d3ec325a4b4bbb00","tid":951136,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpo2dbes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpo2dbes.jpg&h=6fb14ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一艘義大利貨船遭挾持開到英國海域，英國派出海軍菁英「特殊艇部隊」登船奪回。英國特種部隊示意圖。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國東南部海岸外的一艘義大利貨船，遭4名偷渡者挾持，船員們只能將自己鎖在船艙裡待援，英國最後派出海軍特種部隊攻入船艦，制服了4名歹徒，整個行動中沒有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，偷渡者應該是趁貨船在奈及利亞停靠時，找機會溜了上去，並用鋼筋威脅船員把他們載到英國。雖然偷渡者如願到了泰晤士河口外的海域，但英國警方於當地時間21日上午9時（台灣時間21日下午4時）開始介入此案，並通報政府。<br />\n<br />\n英國當局決定出動海軍菁英「特殊艇部隊（Special Boat Service）」，在當地時間21日晚間11時（台灣時間22日上午7時）成功奪回貨船，4名偷渡者則依照移民法被拘留偵訊。經過初步調查，這起事件應與海盜或恐怖主義無關。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2649912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2649912&d=MDE%2Bq9SdTpebmtK%2F5E3Z7wIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=4b8f0fe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2649912&h=5820b031\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2649912</a>"},{"pid":"00b556ca1bf70ed876aedd1ec68ced5190695f9b","tid":951136,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30096f2d00ff5dffa831a72b268231d47b2cebd6","tid":951136,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:10:39.000Z",